description: This perfectly laid out one-bedroom one-bath wastes no space. Although the square footage number presents small.. this condo will leave you stunned. The kitchen is full size and features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and bar height breakfast bar. Living room is bright and sunny with a 6' sliding glass door leading out to private deck with stairs leading up to your own private roof deck. Once up there you will be wowed by the unobstructed and dramatic views of the city. Bedroom has vaulted ceilings and a walk-in closet. Unit is complete with in unit laundry, central air and private deeded storage room in basement. Tenanted til 8/31 but potentially willing to leave early.
